  <brief_title>Immunogenicity, Safety and Tolerability of a Fully Liquid Pentavalent (DTwP-Hib-Hep B) Vaccine in Infants 6-8 Weeks of Age</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase-III, Single Arm, Multi-Center, Open-Label Study to Assess the Immunogenicity, Safety and Tolerability of a Fully Liquid Pentavalent Vaccine (DTwP-Hib-HepB Vaccine) When Administered to Indian Infants at 6, 10, and 14 Weeks of Age</official_title>
